      <title>优步起诉保险公司拒绝承保纽约市车祸司机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/uber-sues-insurer-for-refusing-to-cover-nyc-drivers-in-crashes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[优步科技公司起诉一家汽车责任保险公司，称该保险公司一贯不为发生事故的纽约市共享出行司机承保。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/uber-sues-insurer-for-refusing-to-cover-nyc-drivers-in-crashes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
